trans-unit.source: Represents a single item of data extracted from a workflow and all its associated annotations.
trans-unit.target: Representerar ett enstaka objekt med data som hämtats från ett arbetsflöde och dess associerade anteckningar.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches a track point, it sends a tracking record to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]När spårning körningsinfrastrukturen matchar en TrackPoint, skickar en spårningsposten till Spårningstjänsten.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> may contain <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects that specify data to be extracted from the workflow and returned in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> or the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>eller ett <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>kan innehålla <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>eller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>objekt som anger data som ska extraheras från arbetsflödet och returneras i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>eller i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: A TrackingDataItem represents a single item of this extracted data in either <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: En TrackingDataItem representerar ett enstaka objekt för den här extraherade data i antingen <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the list of annotations associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger listan över anteckningar som är associerade med data som extraheras.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> can specify annotations to be sent with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>eller en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>kan ange anteckningar skickas med data som extraheras.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: These are contained in the Annotations property.
A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref> that contains the annotations associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"> </xref> som innehåller anteckningar som är associerade med data som extraheras.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the extracted data associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den extraherade data som är associerade med den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Data contains the member data, specified by an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>, that was extracted from the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Data innehåller medlemsdata som anges av en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>eller en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>, som har extraherats från arbetsflödesinstansen.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that represents the extracted data.
Gets or sets the name of the property or field associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger namnet på egenskapen eller fältet som är associerade med data som extraheras.

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure supports data extraction on fields and properties of classes that inherit from <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>; a member of such a field or property; and a single item of a field or a property (or a member of either) that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface, for example a single element in a collection.
trans-unit.target: Spårning körningsinfrastrukturen stöder extrahering av data på fält och egenskaper för klasser som ärver från <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>; en medlem av dessa fält eller egenskap, och ett enstaka objekt för ett fält eller en egenskap (eller en medlem i antingen) som implementerar det <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>gränssnitt, till exempel ett element i en samling.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>

trans-unit.source: FieldName contains the dot delineated name of the item extracted and is equivalent to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> depending on which type of extract specified the data contained by the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>.
trans-unit.target: Fältnamn innehåller punkt avgränsad namnet på objektet extraherade och motsvarar <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>eller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>beroende på vilken typ av extrahera angivna data som finns i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>

trans-unit.source: The dot delineated name of the property or field that was extracted.
trans-unit.target: Punkt avgränsad namnet på egenskapen eller fältet som har extraherats.
